    "Note that the Neumann boundary conditions are now not included in the boundary loss L B, as they are already incorporated in the weak form in Eq.",
    "The integrals are evaluated through numerical integration methods, such as Gaussian quadrature, Monte Carlo integration methods [239,240], or sparse grid quadratures [241].",
